lay
over
a
pink
ribbon,
and
was
fastened
with
a
pink
knot.
She
wore
no
other
decoration.
So
much
for
Caroline
Helstone's
appearance.
As
to
her
character
or
intellect,
if
she
had
any,
they
must
speak
